{"tid":540274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每次返屋企入lift嘅時候","createTime":"2018-01-25T10:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T17:21:02.000Z","uid":147591,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"00176c50b0c0a235c6928ab2106e140222569bbc","tid":540274,"uid":147591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"Lift 門閂埋後，如果無人嘅話，我就會哼起歌出嚟，呢個moment係最輕鬆嘅，同埋最有私人空間嘅，有時候喺屋企唱都怕嘈到屋企人，喺lift嘅回音又夠自然，感覺就係自己嘅小舞台。 <br />\n<br />\n有時會好期待嗰短短嘅30秒，加上唔係成日可以自己一個人搭lift，所以我會諗定唱咩歌，心情好唱快歌，心情唔好唱吓慢歌，唱完個人都舒暢啲。<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打，希望你哋都有自己享受嘅小時刻<br />\n有嘅不如分享吓，無嘅可以試下喺lift唱歌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b144d88056f824aaa0055489ac1cd8de6c4187","tid":540274,"uid":94088,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:43:07.000Z","msg":"收工搭貨lift趕到lift門臨關實個刻<br />\n<br />\n開口見到條女合埋眼好enjoy咁係到微un<br />\n<br />\n可能佢塞住個耳機feel唔到有人入左黎<br />\n<br />\n跟手就好似樓主咁開始哼歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哼左幾聲見到原來有人即嚇左一嚇同收聲<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁望住<br />\n<br />\n佢塊面紅到縮埋一角feel到佢想搵窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfe155d1b40fa507df2ec14232284968f01a5c6","tid":540274,"uid":147591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"有無人都會喺lift 唱k"},{"pid":"1fb152f74fa88927280cda5589b04f1e185cc005","tid":540274,"uid":4285,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:49:39.000Z","msg":"放屁之後離開<br />\n<br />\n諗起下個人要聞足全程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3ccd6d8cb6929d8ca7f768cf12f69875ca74a8","tid":540274,"uid":60536,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"成日入lift嗰一刻 首歌咁啱去到純音樂位冇得唱<br />\n好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34115fd72218002bb76371d4a0970f0d4297bcf3","tid":540274,"uid":147591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日入lift嗰一刻 首歌咁啱去到純音樂位冇得唱<br />\n好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過 拉前拉後都係純音樂 最後都唱唔到"},{"pid":"2fea5aab7c7553f38b38aacc51c984eb3b811984","tid":540274,"uid":147591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"推多推"},{"pid":"9faadcc97022b7945ee8c213906ff75fbd50e87e","tid":540274,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"其實管理處可以聽到audio, 係俾其他住戶先cut 咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c624153ccf1773c6ea8c8447f027fd4cdb4ec128","tid":540274,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"569984d73d9c1c6ab123fd20def9fbecfd5f22d2","tid":540274,"uid":125665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"有時一關lift門開始哼就有人即刻禁制開返道門入lift 面對面比佢聽到我哼歌即刻紅都面晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe669aafc13a2cc66e3db126ab54f9fabb7a8da","tid":540274,"uid":10935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9faadcc97022b7945ee8c213906ff75fbd50e87e","tid":540274,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"其實管理處可以聽到audio, 係俾其他住戶先cut 咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:21:02.000Z","msg":"！！！！！！真的嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}